| code_utf8 | desc_varchar_utf8mb4 | code_gbk | code_gb18030 | code_cp932 | code_utf8_unicode_ci |
+-----------+----------------------+----------+--------------+------------+----------------------+
| NULL      | NULL                 | NULL     | NULL         | NULL       | e                    |
+-----------+----------------------+----------+--------------+------------+----------------------+
SELECT * FROM t_multicharset WHERE code_utf8_unicode_ci = '?';
+-----------+----------------------+----------+--------------+------------+----------------------+
